document_data.Notable Cursed Berserking Swords:
* ''[[Enduval]]'', which came to rest in the [[Pyramid of Amun-Re]] as of the mid&ndash;14{{th}} century [[DR]].
* ''[[Helmspitter]]'', a massive and [[sentient]] two-handed sword that came to rest in the horde of [[Storm (red dragon)|Storm]], a young [[red dragon]] in [[the North]].{{Cite dungeon/43/Into The Silver Realm|59}}
* One of the bandit kings of the [[Chieftains in Gold]] wielded a ''cursed berserking longsword'', which earned him a warlike reputation. Upon his death, the blade was interred with him in the [[Tombs of Deckon Thar]].
